;Uses uses WFTypes ; Rule func RentalReimbursementDaysLimit (Limit:Int4):tWFNum8 var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(0, CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.myowner).AppendParam(Limit, 0, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.myowner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') end endFunc
func RentalReimbursementLimitPerDay (Limit:Int4):tWFNum8 var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(1, CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.myowner).AppendParam(Limit, 0, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.myowner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') end endFunc
; Classification ; FieldDesc ; VarDesc
Proc WFCalculate(out Result :tWFNum8) var Memory1 : Num8 var memory2 : Num8 var memory3 : Num8 var NbDaysLimit : Num8 var PerDayLimit : Num8 var LimitGlobal : Num8
Memory1 = 1.32 / 100 LimitGlobal = Option__ItemLimitValue('Rental Reimb. Limit Total') AppendComment(Concat('Rental Reimbursement: Limit: ', NaS(LimitGlobal))) PerDayLimit = Option__ItemLimitValue('Rental Reimb. Limit Per Day') AppendComment(Concat('Rental Reimbursement: Limit per Day: ', NaS(PerDayLimit))) if PerDayLimit <> 0 NbDaysLimit = LimitGlobal / PerDayLimit endIf memory2 = RentalReimbursementDaysLimit(Int4(NbDaysLimit)) memory3 = RentalReimbursementLimitPerDay(Int4(PerDayLimit)) Result = Memory1 * memory3 * memory2 Result = RoundToNearest(Result, 0.01)
end
